  * Merge from debian testing, remaining changes:
    - debian/{control, rules}: Enable PIE hardening.
    - debian/{control, rules, pache2.2-common.ufw.profile}: Add ufw profiles.
    - debian/conrol: Add bzr tag and point it to our tree.
